snippet.title: Castle Cats Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download:
App Store: https://apple.co/3cLGeCF
Google Play Store: https://bit.ly/2WMGoEm
Amazon App Store: https://amzn.to/2X8EIUB

Castle Cats: Epic Story Quests is the best Idle Cat collecting RPG to date. With over 200 different feline heroes, including celebrity cats, to collect and embark on various quests in Catania to battle against the Evil Pugomancer.

Castle Cats lets you become the leader of a guild of cat heroes. Progress idly in your pocket or actively when playing through battles. It is the perfect blend of hero management, cat collecting, and classic RPG storytelling enveloped in a sprinkle of cutesy humor in a free to play-format.
